OL,3,CCampaigners 'horrified' chalk stream
OL,4,Ccould be polluted with sewage
OL,6,FEnvironmental campaigners are
OL,7,F"horrified" that sewage could be
OL,8,Fpumped into the River Test in
OL,9,FHampshire which is famed for its
OL,10,Fdiverse wildlife and fishing.JA
OL,11,Ftemporary pump has been placed at
OL,12,FChilbolton Common near Andover ready
OL,13,Fto release diluted sewage into the
OL,14,Friver as part of an emergency plan to
OL,15,Fprevent flooding.
OL,17,FJames Murray, Actor and Activist
OL,18,FAngler, said: "It drives me mad. I'm
OL,19,Frepresenting 30 river keepers whose
OL,20,Flivelihoods depend on the health of
OL,21,Fthis river.
