OL,3,CCampaigners 'horrified' chalk stream
OL,4,Ccould be polluted with sewage
OL,6,F"You get local people whose raw sewage
OL,7,Fis going to bypass the treatment
OL,8,Fcentre and be pumped straight into a
OL,9,Fchalk stream, jewel of England, river."
OL,11,FSouthern Water says the plan is a
OL,12,F"last resort" and it would only happen
OL,13,Fif groundwater overloads the sewage
OL,14,Fsystem.
OL,16,FThe company says the pipe network is
OL,17,Funder severe pressure, with
OL,18,Fgroundwater making its way into
OL,19,Fsewers, clogging up the system.
