OL,3,CCampaigners 'horrified' chalk stream
OL,4,Ccould be polluted with sewage
OL,6,FAt the moment, Southern Water is using
OL,7,Ftankers to take the excess groundwater
OL,8,Faway, but if the situation gets worse,
OL,9,Fthe company says it will have no
OL,10,Fchoice but to release the overflow
OL,11,Finto the river.
OL,13,FIf Southern Water had to resort to
OL,14,Fover-pumping, there are plans in place
OL,15,Fto also release it into the river at
OL,16,FLongparish, five miles away.
OL,18,FThe River Test is one of around 200
OL,19,Fchalk streams in the world and has
OL,20,Fbeen labelled a site of Special
OL,21,FScientific Interest.
