OL,3,CCampaigners 'horrified' chalk stream
OL,4,Ccould be polluted with sewage
OL,6,FSir David Attenborough described chalk
OL,7,Fstreams as one of the rarest habitats
OL,8,Fon earth.
OL,10,FHoward Taylor, Estate Manager,
OL,11,FFreelands Estate: "Season-wise it's
OL,12,Fjust after the salmon and trout have
OL,13,Fspawned in the river so they have live
OL,14,Feggs in nests in the gravel.
OL,16,F"I'm horrified that none of this has
OL,17,Fbeen taken into account."
