OL,3,CCampaigners 'horrified' chalk stream
OL,4,Ccould be polluted with sewage
OL,6,FGeoff Cooper, Liberal Democrat
OL,7,Fprospective candidate, said: "The
OL,8,Freason that the pipes are flooding
OL,9,Fwith groundwater is because the pipes
OL,10,Fare cracking, it's overwhelming the
OL,11,Fsystem. They need to invest in the
OL,12,Finfrastructure."
OL,14,FIn a statement Southern Water said:
OL,15,F"As part of an emergency plan to
OL,16,Fprevent flooding, we are preparing
OL,17,Foverland pipes to remove groundwater
OL,18,Fand prevent it causing internal
OL,19,Fflooding of homes, schools and
OL,20,Fbusinesses.
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G5/10
