OL,3,CCampaigners 'horrified' chalk stream
OL,4,Ccould be polluted with sewage
OL,6,F"The plan will only be implemented if
OL,7,Fexceptionally high levels of
OL,8,Fgroundwater overload the sewage
OL,9,Fsystem, causing water and sewage to
OL,10,Fenter people's homes.
OL,12,F"The geology of the Chilbolton area is
OL,13,Fhighly vulnerable. The plan, drawn up
OL,14,Fwith co-operation from the Environment
OL,15,FAgency, may see us pump ground water
OL,16,Fout of the sewer and drainage network
OL,17,Fand into nearby watercourses as a last
OL,18,Fresort.
