OL,3,CCampaigners 'horrified' chalk stream
OL,4,Ccould be polluted with sewage
OL,6,F"An impact assessment is currently
OL,7,Fbeing carried out and samples from the
OL,8,Fnetwork and from the area where
OL,9,Freleases may be made, are being
OL,10,Fcollected for analysis."
OL,12,FAlex Saunders, Head of Wastewater
OL,13,FNetworks, said: "We are not using the
OL,14,Fpipes set up to pump into the Test. At
OL,15,Fthe moment tankers are taking excess
OL,16,Fflows away for normal treatment.
