OL,4,Ccould be polluted with sewage
OL,6,F"This plan will only be implemented as
OL,7,Fan absolute last resort to prevent
OL,8,Fflooding within homes, schools and
OL,9,Fbusinesses because groundwater levels
OL,10,Fare exceptionally high and overloading
OL,11,Fthe system.
OL,13,F"It was last used during floods about
OL,14,Fthree years ago and will operate for
OL,15,Fas short a period as possible.
