OL,3,CCampaigners 'horrified' chalk stream
OL,4,Ccould be polluted with sewage
OL,6,F"Releasing highly diluted waste water
OL,7,Finto a watercourse like this is
OL,8,Fsomething we do everything in our
OL,9,Fpower to avoid, but the alternative
OL,10,Fwould mean homes suffering internal
OL,11,Fflooding."
OL,13,FThe Environment Agency said it takes
OL,14,Fover-pumping extremely seriously, and
OL,15,Fif Southern Water do resort to this,
OL,16,Fthen any impacts on local watercourses
OL,17,Fwould be closely monitored.
